The '''Allen & Company Sun Valley Conference''' is an annual media finance conference hosted and wholly independently funded by private investment firm [[Allen & Company]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://dealbook.blogs.nytimes.com/category/sun-valley-2007/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090716031410/http://dealbook.blogs.nytimes.com/category/sun-valley-2007/|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2009-07-16|title=SUN VALLEY 2007 - DealBook Blog - NYTimes.com|date=2009-07-16|access-date=2018-08-03}}</ref> The conference has taken place in [[Sun Valley, Idaho|Sun Valley]], [[Idaho]] for one week each July since 1983.  The gathering typically includes major political figures, business leaders, and figures in the philanthropic and cultural spheres.<ref name="digitaltvlife.com">{{Cite web|url=http://digitaltvlife.com/news/2018/07/12/technology-and-media-vips-gather-at-yearly-sun-valley-conference-2742/|title=Technology and Media VIPs Gather at Yearly Sun Valley Conference - Digital TV Life|website=digitaltvlife.com|language=en-US|access-date=2018-08-03}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.gettyimages.com.au/album/the-annual-summer-camp-for-billionaires-media-tech-and-sports--LnaXrexXdkWRtDBG-hdbCQ#/view-of-the-sun-valley-resort-ahead-of-the-annual-allen-company-sun-picture-id994955978|title=The Annual Summer Camp For Billionaires|work=Getty Images|access-date=2018-08-03|language=en-GB}}</ref>

Previous conference guests have included [[Bill Gates|Bill]] and [[Melinda Gates]], [[Warren Buffett|Warren]] and [[Susan Buffett]],<ref name=":0">{{cite book|title=The Snowball: Warren Buffett and the Business of Life|author=Alice Schroeder|isbn=978-0553805093}}</ref> [[Tony Blair]], [[Google]] founders [[Larry Page]] and [[Sergey Brin]], Allen alumnus and former [[Senate of the Philippines|Philippine Senator]] [[Mar Roxas]], Google Chairman [[Eric Schmidt]], [[Quicken Loans]] Founder & Chairman [[Dan Gilbert]], [[Yahoo!]] co-founder [[Jerry Yang (entrepreneur)|Jerry Yang]], [[Facebook]] founder [[Mark Zuckerberg]], Media Mogul [[Rupert Murdoch]],<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://jafrianews.com/2011/07/09/amid-scandal-murdoch-kills-off-news-of-the-world/murdoch-speaks-briefly-to-the-media-as-he-arrives-the-allen-and-company-sun-valley-conference-in-sun-valley-idaho/|title=Murdoch speaks briefly to the media as he arrives the Allen and Company Sun Valley Conference in Sun Valley, Idaho|date=2011-07-09|work=Jafria News|access-date=2018-08-03|language=en-US}}</ref> [[eBay]] CEO [[Meg Whitman]], [[Black Entertainment Television|BET]] founder [[Robert L. Johnson|Robert Johnson]], [[Time Warner]] Chairman [[Richard Parsons (businessman)|Richard Parsons]], [[Nike, Inc.|Nike]] founder and chairman [[Phil Knight]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://stock.adobe.com/ee/editorial/nike-co-founder-and-chairman-knight-attends-the-second-day-of-the-allen-and-company-sun-valley-conference-in-sun-valley-idaho/156869460|title=Nike co-founder and chairman Knight attends the second day of the Allen and Company Sun Valley Conference in Sun Valley, Idaho - Buy this stock photo and explore similar images at Adobe Stock|website=Adobe Stock|access-date=2018-08-03}}</ref> [[Dell]] founder and CEO [[Michael Dell]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://stock.adobe.com/ee/stock-photo/dell-founder-and-ceo-dell-attends-the-second-day-of-the-allen-and-company-sun-valley-conference-in-sun-valley-idaho/155531691|title=Dell founder and CEO Dell attends the second day of the Allen and Company Sun Valley Conference in Sun Valley, Idaho - Buy this stock photo and explore similar images at Adobe Stock|website=Adobe Stock|access-date=2018-08-03}}</ref> NBA player [[LeBron James]], Governor [[Chris Christie]], [[entertainer]] [[Dan Chandler]], [[Katharine Graham]] of ''[[The Washington Post]]'', [[Diane Sawyer]], [[InterActiveCorp]] Chairman [[Barry Diller]], Linkedin co-founder [[Reid Hoffman]], entrepreneur [[Wences Casares]], [[Exor (company)|EXOR]] and [[Fiat Chrysler Automobiles|FCA]] Chairman [[John Elkann]], [[Sandro Salsano]] from Salsano Group, and Washington Post CEO [[Donald E. Graham]], [[Ivanka Trump]] and [[Jared Kushner]],<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.mercurynews.com/2017/07/14/ivanka-trump-and-jared-kushner-hobnob-in-sun-valley-with-the-tech-and-media-elite-who-rule-our-universe/|title=Ivanka Trump and Jared Kushner hobnob in Sun Valley with the tech and media elite who rule our universe|date=2017-07-14|work=The Mercury News|access-date=2018-08-03|language=en-US}}</ref> and [[Oprah Winfrey]].<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://money.cnn.com/magazines/fortune/fortune_archive/2004/06/28/374371/index.htm|title=Inside the Private World of Allen & Co. Putting a             premium on personal ties, this family firm thrives in the             land of the giants. - June 28, 2004|website=money.cnn.com|access-date=2018-08-03}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://web.presidencia.gov.co/fotos/index.htm|title=Colombia's President Alvaro Uribe attends 2009 Allen & Company Sun Valley Conference|last=|first=|date=|website=Columbian Presidency|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090619205021/http://web.presidencia.gov.co/fotos/index.htm|archive-date=2009-06-19|dead-url=yes|access-date=|df=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://m.boiseweekly.com/boise/allen-and-co-sun-valley-conference-gates-murdoch-and-zuckerbergoh-my/Content?oid=3843595|title=Allen and Co. Sun Valley Conference: Gates, Murdoch and Zuckerberg—Oh My|website=Boise Weekly|language=en-us|access-date=2018-08-03}}</ref><ref name="digitaltvlife.com"/>

Allen & Company is a private investment firm formed in 1922, with headquarters in [[New York City]] and [[London]].  Allen & Company has advised, helped found, and/or invested in companies including [[Black Entertainment Television|BET]], [[InterActiveCorp]], [[Oxygen Media]], [[Discovery Communications]], [[News Corporation]], the [[Coca-Cola Corporation]] and [[Google]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mtexpress.com:80/2004/04-07-02/04-07-02allenco.htm|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120720065820/http://www.mtexpress.com:80/2004/04-07-02/04-07-02allenco.htm|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2012-07-20|title=idaho mountain express : Media moguls alight in valley — Allen + Co opens 22nd annual conference :  Friday, July 2, 2004|date=2012-07-20|access-date=2018-08-03}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mtexpress.com/index2.php?issue_date=07-05-2006&ID=2005111061|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204215634/http://www.mtexpress.com/index2.php?issue_date=07-05-2006&ID=2005111061|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2012-02-04|title=Idaho Mountain Express: Herbert Allen Jr. comes calling again - July 5, 2006|date=2012-02-04|access-date=2018-08-03}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-sunvalley/media-moguls-focus-on-digital-dollars-at-sun-valley-idUSTRE7647B020110706|title=Media moguls focus on digital dollars at Sun Valley|last=Adegoke|first=Yinka|work=U.S.|access-date=2018-08-03|language=en-US}}</ref>

